    <item>
      <title>特朗普法官下令就范尼·威利斯与检察官的事件举行听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/trump-judge-orders-hearing-on-fani-willis-affair-with-prosecutor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佐治亚州一名法官本周下令举行为期两天的听证会，以确定他是否应该取消地区检察官法尼·威利斯参与针对唐纳德·特朗普敲诈勒索案的资格，因为她与首席检察官有恋爱关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/trump-judge-orders-hearing-on-fani-willis-affair-with-prosecutor</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 21:23:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求最高法院暂停华盛顿选举审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/trump-asks-supreme-court-to-keep-dc-criminal-trial-on-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 要求美国最高法院暂停对他试图推翻 2020 年大选的刑事审判，同时他对驳回他申请豁免申请的裁决提出上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/trump-asks-supreme-court-to-keep-dc-criminal-trial-on-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 21:12:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Srettha 与央行的对峙给泰国经济复苏带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/srettha-s-standoff-with-central-bank-risks-thailand-s-economic-turnaround</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国十年来第一位文职领导人上任六个月后，在试图兑现选举承诺、推动经济摆脱十年来低于 2% 的增长率时遇到了障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/srettha-s-standoff-with-central-bank-risks-thailand-s-economic-turnaround</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
